cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.NE 

This paper deals with natural language processing (NLP) and machine learning techniques for entity recognition and classification. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). Additionally, the use of neural networks and deep learning techniques suggests that cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning) are also likely categories. The paper also deals with information retrieval and classification, which could place it in cs.IR (Information Retrieval) and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) categories.
